WEBVTT

00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:03.150
Well, good evening family. Thank you

00:00:03.160 --> 00:00:04.630
for joining us.

00:00:07.360 --> 00:00:09.910
Again, I have an urgency to pray all

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:12.270
the time. I feel it's

00:00:12.280 --> 00:00:13.745
been my

00:00:14.560 --> 00:00:16.990
MO, I guess, my

00:00:16.990 --> 00:00:17.000
modus operandi.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:19.830
It's been very intense lately. And you

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:22.070
know, I'm so thankful that every one

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:23.910
of you would come on at this late hour

00:00:23.910 --> 00:00:23.920
of the

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:25.870
night to pray with me. There

00:00:25.870 --> 00:00:25.880
are

00:00:25.880 --> 00:00:29.030
1,400 of you so

00:00:29.040 --> 00:00:31.590
quickly. And I know I go on all

00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:33.750
over the world and probably not a lot

00:00:33.760 --> 00:00:36.230
of Americans are up at this time,

00:00:36.240 --> 00:00:38.670
but this is the time I pray a lot. So,

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:41.870
I just always come on with y'all and

00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:43.790
it feels like we get a lot

00:00:43.800 --> 00:00:45.750
accomplished very quickly,

00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:48.870
for many hands make light work. Let's

00:00:48.880 --> 00:00:51.870
go over some of the things the Lord said in

00:00:51.870 --> 00:00:51.880
the

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:53.470
last video

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:55.830
and what we saw. I won't go over the

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:58.070
prophetic word. Diana said

00:00:58.080 --> 00:01:00.430
it was five to ten

00:01:00.430 --> 00:01:00.440
pages—ten

00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:03.070
pages, five front and

00:01:03.070 --> 00:01:03.080
back—of

00:01:03.080 --> 00:01:04.670
everything the Lord said. If you have

00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:07.590
not watched that video, go to the

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:10.750
last part of the last video we did.

00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:12.590
That word was very powerful from the

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:14.510
Father. It was one of those words that

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:16.270
will forever

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:20.110
change your life; it shook us.

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:25.070
This whole thing, like I said,

00:01:25.070 --> 00:01:25.080
is...

00:01:25.080 --> 00:01:27.230
these times are so precious

00:01:27.240 --> 00:01:29.310
that we're living in right now,

00:01:29.320 --> 00:01:30.550
and

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:32.390
we have a lot of work to do in

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.990
the spirit realm.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:37.270
First off, I want to say this:

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:39.750
taking communion before you pray and

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:41.670
keeping strife out of your

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:44.750
house—keeping

00:01:44.760 --> 00:01:48.270
the flow. You must walk in love

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:50.390
in these last days.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:51.990
I keep saying that over and over again

00:01:51.990 --> 00:01:52.000
because

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:53.390
of the things the Lord keeps

00:01:53.400 --> 00:01:56.070
bringing up to me. Don't give place to

00:01:56.080 --> 00:01:58.670
the devil at all in your house.

00:01:58.680 --> 00:02:02.110
Keep strife out of your house.

00:02:02.120 --> 00:02:03.470
I know it's easier

00:02:03.480 --> 00:02:05.470
said than done some days,

00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:07.350
but I'm trying to warn you by things

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:11.390
that I got tonight that you must stay in

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:13.630
a constant flow of the presence of God

00:02:13.640 --> 00:02:16.390
and love. Make love a priority in your

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:17.750
home.

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:20.230
Above everything else, keep love

00:02:20.230 --> 00:02:20.240
a

00:02:20.240 --> 00:02:21.390
priority.

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:24.230
So, let's go over what I

00:02:24.240 --> 00:02:28.230
saw yesterday. I saw Mickey Mouse.

00:02:28.240 --> 00:02:29.470
Everybody said, 'What's the

00:02:29.470 --> 00:02:29.480
mouse?'Mickey

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:30.670
Mouse.

00:02:30.680 --> 00:02:32.910
I saw Orlando.

00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:34.510
I saw

00:02:34.520 --> 00:02:38.310
the Lord showed us Tron,

00:02:38.320 --> 00:02:40.190
which is a ride

00:02:40.200 --> 00:02:41.510
in

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:44.230
Magic Kingdom.

00:02:44.240 --> 00:02:48.430
I saw security guards

00:02:48.440 --> 00:02:49.590
and that was what I thought was

00:02:49.600 --> 00:02:52.550
interesting; it was highlighted to me.

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:55.270
Did I see them doing anything?

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:58.430
No. The Lord said

00:02:58.440 --> 00:03:01.150
to pray over Orlando. So, you can

00:03:01.160 --> 00:03:03.270
automatically kind of put things

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:06.110
together without Him coming on directly

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:08.150
and exposing everything. Maybe He'll

00:03:08.160 --> 00:03:10.510
show us more tonight, maybe not. But He

00:03:10.520 --> 00:03:12.390
was showing security guards that

00:03:12.400 --> 00:03:14.310
had infiltrated

00:03:14.320 --> 00:03:18.150
the security system of Disney, these

00:03:18.720 --> 00:03:20.350
evildoers.

00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:23.310
And the Lord said, 'Pray for

00:03:23.310 --> 00:03:23.320
Disney.'I

00:03:23.320 --> 00:03:25.510
saw Asian

00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:27.150
women,

00:03:27.150 --> 00:03:27.160
tourists,

00:03:27.160 --> 00:03:30.270
walking around with Mickey Mouse

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:31.550
ears.

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:33.270
They were walking around and I saw

00:03:33.270 --> 00:03:33.280
a

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:36.950
little go-kart area,

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:39.870
and I saw Tron, and I saw an

00:03:39.870 --> 00:03:39.880
area—I

00:03:39.880 --> 00:03:41.670
don't know why that area was highlighted

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:42.790
to

00:03:42.790 --> 00:03:42.800
me—but

00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:45.190
the Lord showed me this area in

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:46.910
Magic Kingdom

00:03:46.920 --> 00:03:48.350
and the Lord said, 'You need to pray

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:49.950
for

00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:52.390
this.'I

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:57.310
could see it was faded

00:03:57.320 --> 00:03:59.190
out; it was

00:04:03.960 --> 00:04:06.590
blurred. This is what

00:04:06.600 --> 00:04:08.070
this looked like. It was blurred out

00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:09.590
before the vision and they were

00:04:09.600 --> 00:04:11.630
coming, but I didn't know what they were

00:04:11.640 --> 00:04:14.510
going to do. There was darkness that

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:16.550
was

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:18.270
involved around this, and that's what

00:04:18.280 --> 00:04:21.310
the Lord said: 'Pray.'So, I saw that,

00:04:21.320 --> 00:04:24.910
and then yesterday I came on

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:27.470
and I told you I've had an urgency and

00:04:27.480 --> 00:04:29.990
I've been praying all day.

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:32.230
After it was over, when I came on

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:34.430
here,

00:04:36.640 --> 00:04:39.590
the burden to pray was lifting.

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:41.390
But I thought, 'Well, I'll bring it to

00:04:41.400 --> 00:04:42.750
the public

00:04:42.760 --> 00:04:45.430
and we'll pray as a family together,

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:47.590
and we'll make a lot of this

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:49.190
really quickly.'We'll just

00:04:49.200 --> 00:04:51.350
knock this thing out because I told

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:52.230
you,

00:04:52.230 --> 00:04:52.240
Pais,

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:54.310
we were all in deep intercession

00:04:54.320 --> 00:04:55.830
all afternoon.

00:04:55.840 --> 00:04:58.590
I told Diana,

00:04:58.600 --> 00:05:01.430
'I've never felt that intense

00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:04.750
prayer in a long

00:05:04.750 --> 00:05:04.760
time.'It

00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:06.430
was so intense that you almost

00:05:06.440 --> 00:05:08.990
felt nauseous.

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:11.070
You

00:05:11.080 --> 00:05:13.670
knew it was something very dark.

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:16.630
Well, I got out of here

00:05:18.520 --> 00:05:21.030
that evening and I said last night,

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:23.350
'Father, what was that?

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:24.550
Why

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:25.990
did it lift like that? Can you

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:29.430
explain to me what the intensity

00:05:29.430 --> 00:05:29.440
was?'And

00:05:29.440 --> 00:05:31.270
then He said, 'The

00:05:31.280 --> 00:05:34.950
event

00:05:34.950 --> 00:05:34.960
happened.'He

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:36.590
said, 'Brandon, there's no reason, no

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:39.150
need anymore to try to stop it if it

00:05:39.150 --> 00:05:39.160
is

00:05:39.160 --> 00:05:41.950
already

00:05:41.950 --> 00:05:41.960
manifested.'He

00:05:41.960 --> 00:05:43.710
said, 'What you were praying over all

00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:45.710
day was the event that took place in

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:48.550
California at the birthday

00:05:48.550 --> 00:05:48.560
party.'What

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:51.110
you were praying for and

00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:53.030
interceding for—and why Paisley was so

00:05:53.030 --> 00:05:53.040
involved—my

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:56.110
little girl was interceding

00:05:56.120 --> 00:05:59.790
for the children. She was in travail,

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:01.710
and I would say, 'What is a little girl

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:03.990
like this travailing over this? What is

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:05.670
this?'But

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:07.590
she said, 'Daddy, I feel I

00:06:07.600 --> 00:06:09.350
got to pray. I got to pray.'And

00:06:09.350 --> 00:06:09.360
she's just

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:10.510
praying in tongues,

00:06:10.520 --> 00:06:12.750
travailing in the spirit,

00:06:12.760 --> 00:06:14.790
laying hands on her brother,

00:06:14.800 --> 00:06:16.590
praying over Braden, and praying

00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:18.470
over Mama. She goes, 'I'm just

00:06:18.470 --> 00:06:18.480
praying.'Like

00:06:18.480 --> 00:06:20.630
I

00:06:20.640 --> 00:06:22.750
said, it was the most intense, and

00:06:22.760 --> 00:06:25.390
she was praying as loud as she

00:06:25.400 --> 00:06:28.590
possibly could as a little girl.

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:30.470
Finally, I said, 'Are you done,

00:06:30.480 --> 00:06:31.510
hun?'because

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:33.750
I was going to go get us a drink.

00:06:33.760 --> 00:06:35.270
And she goes, 'No, Daddy, it's not done

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:36.510
yet. We got to keep praying.'And she

00:06:36.520 --> 00:06:38.950
kept praying and praying, and

00:06:38.960 --> 00:06:41.190
we were all

00:06:41.200 --> 00:06:43.350
backing her and praying with her.

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:44.950
But I thought, 'What is this on my

00:06:44.960 --> 00:06:46.670
little girl?

00:06:46.680 --> 00:06:47.910
Holy Spirit, You're pulling

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:49.750
her?'I

00:06:49.760 --> 00:06:51.910
thought it was really interesting.

00:06:51.920 --> 00:06:54.430
Whenever Paisley prays,

00:06:54.440 --> 00:06:56.510
she's a great intercessor. We're

00:06:56.520 --> 00:06:59.310
training her, like

00:06:59.320 --> 00:07:02.710
all our kids, Braden and Paisley. If

00:07:02.710 --> 00:07:02.720
and

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:04.510
when Megan becomes

00:07:04.510 --> 00:07:04.520
a

00:07:04.520 --> 00:07:06.390
manifestation of her—I can't wait to

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:09.950
see what God does with her

00:07:09.950 --> 00:07:09.960
because

00:07:09.960 --> 00:07:11.430
I know there's giftings there; she's

00:07:11.440 --> 00:07:14.230
my

00:07:15.230 --> 00:07:15.240
firstborn—but

00:07:16.040 --> 00:07:18.830
when Paisley was interceding like that,

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:20.550
it felt like it lifted a little bit. Then

00:07:20.560 --> 00:07:21.590
we came home and started praying

00:07:21.600 --> 00:07:22.670
some more,

00:07:22.680 --> 00:07:26.030
but as I brought it to you all,

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:28.910
it lifted,

00:07:28.920 --> 00:07:32.670
but it was already done.

00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:34.630
It was already done, and four

00:07:34.640 --> 00:07:37.630
children lost their lives.

00:07:37.640 --> 00:07:40.230
It was interesting.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:44.030
Every time I see a tragic event happen,

00:07:44.040 --> 00:07:46.590
I look at it as a prayer fail.

00:07:46.600 --> 00:07:48.950
I told you Saturday, I saw

00:07:48.960 --> 00:07:51.710
14 people.

00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:55.630
The Lord kept telling me Saturday about

00:07:55.630 --> 00:07:55.640
14—'You

00:07:55.640 --> 00:07:58.790
must intercede for Saturday

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:02.310
for 14, there's an event.'Well, quite

00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:04.110
frankly, with all the things that I get on

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:06.150
a day-to-day basis, we take note of it,

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:08.670
but I had forgotten about it.

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:10.550
I had forgotten about it because it

00:08:10.550 --> 00:08:10.560
was three days

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:12.550
prior, and I've been praying over

00:08:12.550 --> 00:08:12.560
the

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:14.070
President—very

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:16.750
intense prayer concerning the White

00:08:16.760 --> 00:08:19.670
House and the trees and the lighting

00:08:19.670 --> 00:08:19.680
ceremonies—praying

00:08:19.680 --> 00:08:21.550
for our nation's

00:08:21.560 --> 00:08:24.630
capital because of what the Lord told me

00:08:24.640 --> 00:08:27.790
of

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:30.190
a new D-Day. And He's bringing up a new

00:08:30.200 --> 00:08:33.149
D-Day, a new Red Dawn experience. And He

00:08:33.159 --> 00:08:35.870
said, 'Brandon, they couldn't get you

00:08:35.880 --> 00:08:38.469
like D-Day because of how far you are

00:08:38.479 --> 00:08:40.990
away from them, so they invaded you

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:43.550
like a Trojan

00:08:43.550 --> 00:08:43.560
horse.'For

00:08:43.560 --> 00:08:48.310
there are many, many men and women

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:50.870
in your nation that have come

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:53.350
over illegally, that have infiltrated

00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:55.950
your cities in every single

00:08:55.960 --> 00:08:58.310
state. Every state.

00:08:58.320 --> 00:09:01.070
He said it is an infestation

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:05.350
of the brotherhood of terrorist

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:08.070
activity. And then He warned me.

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:12.830
He said, 'Do not stereotype.

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:15.790
You are looking for a certain individual

00:09:15.790 --> 00:09:15.800
and

00:09:15.800 --> 00:09:18.030
the way they

00:09:18.030 --> 00:09:18.040
look.'He

00:09:18.040 --> 00:09:20.550
said,

00:09:25.680 --> 00:09:27.190
'They're right in front of

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:28.870
your face; they're not

00:09:29.950 --> 00:09:29.960
hidden.'I

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:33.830
don't want to misquote it; Braden had

00:09:33.840 --> 00:09:37.190
to look up the archive. But

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:39.950
the Lord was specifically saying

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:42.070
just because they have dark skin and a

00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:45.670
beard doesn't mean that's the

00:09:45.670 --> 00:09:45.680
only way they're used.

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:47.510
These are

00:09:47.520 --> 00:09:50.030
even white people, black people,

00:09:50.040 --> 00:09:52.430
Mexican,

00:09:52.430 --> 00:09:52.440
Asian—that's

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:53.910
all part of the brotherhood. Just

00:09:53.920 --> 00:09:55.870
because they don't look Arab or

00:09:57.440 --> 00:09:58.910
Middle Eastern,

00:10:00.240 --> 00:10:02.030
don't stereotype just because you think

00:10:02.040 --> 00:10:03.830
that's only the way

00:10:03.840 --> 00:10:06.070
they're going to be used.

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:08.190
The Lord said they have infiltrated

00:10:08.200 --> 00:10:11.190
even your government.

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:13.230
He said, "They're in your police force.

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:16.510
They're in your top tier

00:10:16.520 --> 00:10:18.070
of the

00:10:18.070 --> 00:10:18.080
Pentagon."He

00:10:18.080 --> 00:10:21.910
even warned about our FBI, all

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:24.030
of it. He told us there are rats within;

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:26.750
he keeps talking about the rats within.

00:10:26.760 --> 00:10:29.670
So, I want to encourage you.

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:31.830
We're looking for anybody who is

00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:34.150
a bogeyman. I want to say

00:10:34.160 --> 00:10:35.910
don't always think that it's going to

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:37.430
be somebody with a turban on their

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:38.790
head or

00:10:38.790 --> 00:10:38.800
a

00:10:38.800 --> 00:10:41.110
full dress or whatever that that's the

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:43.470
enemy, because the people

00:10:43.480 --> 00:10:46.270
that were infiltrating into the

00:10:46.270 --> 00:10:46.280
country

00:10:46.280 --> 00:10:47.710
were not

00:10:47.720 --> 00:10:49.550
Arab-looking.

00:10:49.560 --> 00:10:51.430
They were white.

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:53.310
And I thought it was interesting

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:54.750
because this is what the Spirit of the

00:10:54.760 --> 00:10:56.430
Lord is telling us to pray for our

00:10:56.440 --> 00:10:57.870
nation again.

00:10:57.880 --> 00:11:00.510
And people say, "Who are

00:11:00.510 --> 00:11:00.520
they?"They

00:11:00.520 --> 00:11:01.710
keep asking me—even the police

00:11:01.720 --> 00:11:03.030
officers ask me when I

00:11:03.040 --> 00:11:05.350
talk to the big

00:11:05.350 --> 00:11:05.360
people—they

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:06.790
always go, "Brandon, you always say

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:08.670
they? Who's they?

00:11:08.680 --> 00:11:12.030
Who's they to you? Why do you say they?""They"refers

00:11:12.030 --> 00:11:12.040
to

00:11:12.040 --> 00:11:15.630
all of it combined.

00:11:15.640 --> 00:11:17.670
What does that mean to me? The devil

00:11:17.680 --> 00:11:19.870
worshippers that I see,

00:11:19.870 --> 00:11:19.880
the

